body:
@ashokvishnoi1994 Some documentation does help. But if you want to get some quick information, you can try something like this: 
```python
with tf.Session(graph=tf.Graph()) as sess:
    input, predictions = tf.import_graph_def(g, return_elements=
                                                     ['Input:0', 
                                                      'Predictions/Reshape_1:0'])
    p_val = predictions.eval(feed_dict={input: image})
```
where you need to know the name of input node and output node when you freeze the graph.
